query:
SELECT
            books.*,
            books_text.name,
            percent,
            book_series_text.name series_name
        FROM
            books
        NATURAL INNER JOIN
            books_percent
        INNER JOIN
            books_text
        ON
            books.id = books_text.id AND books_text.language = $1
        INNER JOIN
            book_series
        ON
            series = book_series.id
        INNER JOIN
            book_series_text
        ON
            series = book_series_text.id AND book_series_text.language = $1
        ORDER BY
            id
